{"tid":536524,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小球童贊C朗是世界最佳，C朗回應：美斯是差的","createTime":"2018-01-22T00:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T12:54:01.000Z","uid":1090,"like":203,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba5cdbf53891415a854a7bf0abdb7d4c2a55ace","tid":536524,"uid":1090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"在今天凌晨的西甲聯賽中，皇馬7-1大勝拉科魯尼亞，C朗也結束了球荒在比賽中梅開二度。而在賽前的球員通道，攝像機抓拍到了C朗和小球童之間的有趣談話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在比賽前幾分鐘的球員通道，小球童們和皇馬球員們交流著，一個小球童對葡萄牙人說道：「對我來說你是世界最佳！而美斯...（Para m&iacute; eres el mejor del mundo y Messi es....）」這時C朗笑著接話道：「是差的...（es malo）」而旁邊另一個小球童則起哄道：「最差的！最差的！（el peor，el peor）」而後C朗和幾個隊友輕輕笑了下，等待著進場的命令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02763b35a46a9fcc7fa53e4a04ee65e371c1ba69","tid":536524,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a642ec91d140a191011f4e1c3cb846fedbc086f4","tid":536524,"uid":19552,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"最緊要大家開心"},{"pid":"e7203be3561a9e3900d6fb8b9922551f5d938859","tid":536524,"uid":1367,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:54:24.000Z","msg":"牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c957969bf83938b52a9be7c8a3371ea1120d1535","tid":536524,"uid":54712,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:54:48.000Z","msg":"笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fc27ee51064025a5ac9bb5c79f30ce3eb800ed","tid":536524,"uid":34419,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"牙朗開心滿足咪得"},{"pid":"dcf06d45eb50957401824d1f215e24b85c