core":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在今天凌晨的西甲聯賽中，皇馬7-1大勝拉科魯尼亞，C朗也結束了球荒在比賽中梅開二度。而在賽前的球員通道，攝像機抓拍到了C朗和小球童之間的有趣談話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在比賽前幾分鐘的球員通道，小球童們和皇馬球員們交流著，一個小球童對葡萄牙人說道：「<span style=\"color: red;\">對我來說</span>你是世界最佳！而美斯...（Para m&iacute; eres el mejor del mundo y Messi es....）」這時C朗笑著接話道：「是差的...（es malo）」而旁邊另一個小球童則起哄道：「最差的！最差的！（el peor，el peor）」而後C朗和幾個隊友輕輕笑了下，等待著進場的命令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小朋友都知咩事啦，要安慰牙朗弱小心靈"},{"pid":"190a98955db6d8ea68a4ae9880d94826c60cf07c","tid":536524,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"球王c朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfa2a5ff1e81c9df84c3dce639214d5ec19482b","tid":536524,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"小朋友算厚道，唔講垃圾講差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b90433769a8e559d69b82be62e17e4ef46e527","tid":536524,"uid":150780,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"點睇都似係同細路仔玩下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef35db6c1b4e8ae4d937a640a95f7a6145dd5b8","tid":536524,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900ce51c4aeb19d746bac6fccf45e8cdd7880780","tid":536524,"uid":993,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8dc02b82deea0be9979f9b0